# aisopod-channel-{{name}}

{{display_name}} channel plugin for aisopod.

## Overview

This crate provides a {{display_name}} channel implementation for aisopod, enabling the bot to
receive and send messages via the {{display_name}} platform.

## Features

- Incoming message reception
- Outgoing message sending
- Connection management
- Error handling

## Setup

1. Add this crate to your aisopod workspace members in `Cargo.toml`:
   ```toml
   members = [
       # ...
       "crates/aisopod-channel-{{name}}",
   ]
   ```

2. Enable the plugin in `aisopod-plugin`:
   ```toml
   [features]
   plugin-{{name}} = ["dep:aisopod-channel-{{name}}"]
   
   [dependencies]
   aisopod-channel-{{name}} = { path = "../aisopod-channel-{{name}}", optional = true }
   ```

3. Build: `cargo build -p aisopod-channel-{{name}}`

## Configuration

Add the following to your aisopod config file:

```toml
[[channels]]
id = "{{name}}"
name = "{{display_name}}"
channel_type = "{{name}}"
connection = { endpoint = "", token = "" }
```

